'Title: Misleading Packaging - Disappointing Shirt Condition'
body: I already have this type of shirt but of different colours.I had high hopes for this shirt, but my experience fell short. The shirt arrived sealed, but upon opening, I found it used with visible white spots and marks.  Pros: 1. Design: The design and color matched the listing.  Cons: 1. Condition: The shirt's condition was disappointing with noticeable stains. 2. Packaging: The sealed packaging was misleading. 3. Overall Disappointment: Not recommended due to the inaccurate presentation.
